Interp: The demon, represented by metal in the monkey branch, as the significator, is disrupted by the day's establishing clash and is also weakened by the activation and vulnerability of the six lines in the dog branch, which is unfavorable.

Q: Will the man's pursuit of his lover succeed?
A: It won't work out.
Interp: Wife and Wealth Wood in Yin is initially a favorable element in a prosperous state, but it gets activated, and then further enhanced by the Demons Fire in Wu, which moves and transforms to drain and benefit the world line. Wife and Wealth Wood in Yin thus plays a negative role in the hexagram.

Q: How to successfully set up a stall somewhere? Can it be approved or not?
A: The changing line of Children indicates that the matter may eventually succeed, but the current resistance is significant, requiring flexible responses. It is advised to prepare documentation in advance, communicate with relevant departments, and strive to submit the application at a favorable opportunity.
Interp: The hexagram is unfavorable. Although the Children line is active, it is subject to emptiness, which may hinder the handling of the stall-related matters. It is advised to make thorough preparations and patiently wait for the right opportunity before taking action.

Q: Is the annual vehicle inspection at the vehicle management office going well?
A: The vehicle's annual inspection was successfully processed.
Interp: Parents with You gold serving as the favorable useful spirit move to give life to the self line, which is auspicious.

Q: Will this business cooperation be successful?
A: Because the demons fire of Si is an unfavorable god, cooperation is difficult to achieve and progress is slow.
Interp: The responsive line pertains to the other party. The responsive line "Demons" represented by si fire is in a void during the ten-day cycle, but it aligns and prospers by the month's establishment, moving to generate the self line.
